      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t中華民國滅共除殖行動大隊 隊旗<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYjhlMTFjMDk3NzVkZTRkNDc1NTAyLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b8e11c09775de4d475502.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b8e11c09775de4d475502.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b8e11c09775de4d475502.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n不是引蛇出洞，到了最后关头再去灭共，也不用杀党员，把党员们的狗眼戳瞎就好，多戳几只。\t\t</div>",
